faqList.question: How can I get a refund?

docArticles.title: googi Size Guide
docArticles.content:
# googi Size Guide

Finding your perfect fit makes every outfit feel right.

Here’s how googi helps you choose the ideal size — along with fit details for our three signature pieces.

---

## 1. Our General Fit Philosophy

googi follows **Korean standard sizing** but uses slightly relaxed silhouettes for comfort and natural drape.

Most tops fit true to size; bottoms are designed for a soft, straight fall.

If you’re between sizes, we recommend **going one size up** for a more effortless fit.

---

## 2. Core Products & Fit Details

### 👕 googi Standard Fit Shirt

- A versatile daily shirt with minimal seams
- Fit: Regular (comfortable across shoulders and chest)
- Size tip: Choose your normal size; if you prefer a looser fit, go one size up
- Fabric: 100% linen cotton blend

---

### 👔 googi Oversized Collar Shirt

- Signature oversized silhouette with drop shoulders
- Fit: Loose (intentionally relaxed shape)
- Size tip: For a cleaner look, size down; for a true oversized style, pick your usual size
- Fabric: Premium linen, pre-washed to prevent shrinkage

---

### 🧥 googi Linen Blazer

- Lightweight linen blazer, structured but breathable
- Fit: Semi-tailored (shoulders structured, waist slightly loose)
- Size tip: Stick to your usual size for layering; upsize for a more casual summer fit
- Fabric: Linen 60%, rayon 40%

---

## 3. Measurement Reference (in cm)

| Size | Shoulder | Chest | Sleeve | Length |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| S | 45 | 52 | 60 | 72 |
| M | 47 | 55 | 61 | 74 |
| L | 49 | 58 | 62 | 76 |

---

## 4. How to Measure Yourself

1. Use a soft measuring tape
2. Measure across your favorite shirt laid flat
3. Compare your numbers with the chart above

---

Finding your googi fit should feel easy and confident —

because the best outfit is the one that fits *you* perfectly.

docArticles.title: googi Gift Option

Here’s how googi wraps your appreciation beautifully.

docArticles.title: googi Shipping Policy
docArticles.content:
# Shipping & Delivery

We ship fast and carefully to make sure your googi order arrives in perfect shape.

---

## Schedule
- Ships within **2–3 business days** after payment  
- Orders before 2 PM usually go out the same day  
- No shipments on weekends or holidays  

---

## Fees & Regions
- Standard shipping: **₩3,000** (free over ₩50,000)  
- Jeju / Islands: 1–2 extra days  
- Courier: CJ Logistics  

---

## Delays
Severe weather or logistics issues may cause delays.  
We’ll notify you by text or email in such cases.

---

Even a single shirt deserves our fastest, safest delivery.

docArticles.title: Linen Care Guide
docArticles.content:
# Linen Care Guide

Linen — the timeless summer fabric.  
It’s breathable and light, but also delicate. With a little care, it stays beautiful for years.

---

## Before Washing
- Wash separately the first few times  
- Use **cold water (below 30°C)** with mild detergent  
- Avoid alkaline or bleach products

---

## Washing Steps
1. **Hand-wash gently** or use a laundry net on a delicate cycle  
2. Keep spin-dry short (under 30 seconds)  
3. **Air dry in shade**, avoid direct sunlight  

---

## Ironing
- Press while slightly damp, using **medium heat**  
- Steam helps relax natural wrinkles  

---

Note: Linen’s **1–2% shrinkage** is a natural characteristic — it’s what gives that relaxed silhouette we all love.

docArticles.title: googi Refund Policy
docArticles.content:
# googi Refund & Exchange Policy

Your satisfaction means everything to us.  
If your purchase doesn’t fit or you simply change your mind, we’ll make returns easy.

---

## Refunds
- Available within **7 days** of receiving your order  
- Item and packaging must remain in **original condition**  
- Refunds are processed within **3–5 business days**  
- *Sale or promotion items are non-refundable*

---

## Exchanges
- Same product exchanges for **color or size**  
- Round-trip shipping fee: **₩6,000 (₩3,000 each way)**  
- If the product is defective or incorrect, googi covers all shipping costs

---

## How to Request
1. Go to **My Page → Orders → Refund/Exchange Request**  
2. Upload photos and briefly explain the reason  
3. A courier will collect the package and we’ll handle the rest

---

We take every customer concern seriously — thank you for trusting googi.
